name: Bootstrap 5
description:
Components make use of the latest version of auto layout and variants and will be updated as Figma ships new features.


Also includes color styles


The Bootstrap CSS uses system-ui font, which will be different on different operating systems. The font used in this file is therefore different from what you will see in a web browser.


Unlike other component libraries, you will not experience any annoying "missing font" dialog messages.


See also the Figma Community Bootstrap Icons file https://www.figma.com/community/file/972989644486753519/Bootstrap-Icons-v1.5.0
